WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:02.133
Hello, welcome back to Bai Xiaojun's channel. In the

00:00:02.333 --> 00:00:05.099
previous two episodes, I introduced

00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:06.933
some key points about Shopify operations

00:00:06.933 --> 00:00:08.566
and its product selection methods.

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.333
Today, this video will mainly talk about

00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:13.866
how to design our product landing pages,

00:00:13.866 --> 00:00:16.566
also known as product detail pages.

00:00:17.133 --> 00:00:18.299
Product detail pages

00:00:18.300 --> 00:00:20.733
are mainly related to our conversion rate.

00:00:21.133 --> 00:00:23.333
A beautiful and high-quality detail page

00:00:23.333 --> 00:00:25.766
can not only bring us high conversion rates,

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.666
but also increase our average order value.

00:00:28.966 --> 00:00:29.933
It can help

00:00:29.933 --> 00:00:32.899
buyers discover more highlights while browsing our website,

00:00:32.900 --> 00:00:34.866


00:00:34.866 --> 00:00:36.933
including some information about our store,

00:00:36.966 --> 00:00:40.466
and build trust with buyers, etc.

00:00:40.466 --> 00:00:41.666
Okay, without further ado,

00:00:41.666 --> 00:00:42.699
let's take a look at

00:00:42.700 --> 00:00:45.466
the basic elements that a detail page should have.

00:00:50.300 --> 00:00:51.766
First is our main image.

00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:53.566
When visitors enter our website, the

00:00:53.566 --> 00:00:55.899
first thing they see is our main image.

00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:58.566
If we are running a brand store

00:00:58.566 --> 00:01:00.099
or a boutique store,

00:01:00.333 --> 00:01:03.166
we should try to maintain a

00:01:03.166 --> 00:01:05.066
sense of technology or style for our main image.

00:01:05.600 --> 00:01:07.200
Generally,

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:08.800
we use a white background

00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:12.566
or our website's theme color as the background for the first main image.

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:14.600
This not only maintains the

00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:16.100
unified style of the store,

00:01:16.133 --> 00:01:17.066
but also

00:01:17.066 --> 00:01:19.766
highlights the overall style of our website.

00:01:19.766 --> 00:01:22.466
As for the subsequent main images,

00:01:22.466 --> 00:01:24.133
we can use

00:01:24.366 --> 00:01:26.533
photos that resemble scenes.

00:01:26.533 --> 00:01:29.499
Or, to put it another way, photos that describe some of its features.

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:31.566
Of course, if you have the resources and skills,

00:01:31.566 --> 00:01:32.666
you can

00:01:32.666 --> 00:01:34.599
create rendered images like this, which would

00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:36.133
look much more sophisticated.

00:01:36.133 --> 00:01:38.399
However, if you're running a mass-market

00:01:38.566 --> 00:01:41.199
store focusing on value for money,

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:43.133
I think simple, lifestyle-oriented photos like these are

00:01:43.133 --> 00:01:44.899
sufficient.

00:01:44.933 --> 00:01:45.799
You can't expect to have

00:01:45.800 --> 00:01:47.866
so many products in one store, and

00:01:47.866 --> 00:01:48.366


00:01:48.366 --> 00:01:51.166
each product image to be exquisitely crafted.

00:01:51.366 --> 00:01:54.699
After the images is the product title.

00:01:54.700 --> 00:01:56.900
Regardless of whether you're using Shopify

00:01:56.900 --> 00:01:58.066
or WordPress,

00:01:58.300 --> 00:02:00.333
you actually have two titles. The top

00:02:00.466 --> 00:02:01.399
title

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:04.266
is displayed on the front end of your website

00:02:04.266 --> 00:02:05.299
for buyers to see.

00:02:05.300 --> 00:02:07.700
We should keep it concise, simply

00:02:07.700 --> 00:02:09.966
telling buyers what we're selling.

00:02:09.966 --> 00:02:12.266
For example, the

00:02:12.266 --> 00:02:13.666
title of this website is this.

00:02:13.733 --> 00:02:16.899
Below that is an SEO title and description.

00:02:17.333 --> 00:02:20.733
This part is mainly for search engines.

00:02:20.733 --> 00:02:22.866
When we run certain ads,

00:02:22.966 --> 00:02:25.399
they will automatically extract keywords from our title and description.

00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:27.100


00:02:27.100 --> 00:02:27.900
So,

00:02:28.100 --> 00:02:31.000
we need to fill this part out

00:02:31.366 --> 00:02:34.533
carefully, trying to include some keywords,

00:02:34.533 --> 00:02:37.499
including information about our website, etc. The

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:39.566
purposes of these two titles are different,

00:02:39.566 --> 00:02:41.499
so we

00:02:41.500 --> 00:02:42.600
need to pay attention when filling them out. The

00:02:42.600 --> 00:02:45.333
third part is product reviews.

00:02:45.666 --> 00:02:48.166
Reviews are very important for products.

00:02:48.166 --> 00:02:51.099
Most buyers

00:02:51.466 --> 00:02:54.133
consult other people's opinions before purchasing,

00:02:54.666 --> 00:02:55.899
just like when we buy things ourselves.

00:02:55.900 --> 00:02:56.933


00:02:57.200 --> 00:02:59.133
Besides considering the price,

00:02:59.133 --> 00:03:02.666
reviews are also a very important reference indicator. When adding reviews for

00:03:02.666 --> 00:03:04.966
products on our website, we should try to

00:03:04.966 --> 00:03:06.199


00:03:06.200 --> 00:03:07.700


00:03:07.700 --> 00:03:10.766
refer to reviews of similar or identical products on Amazon,

00:03:11.166 --> 00:03:12.599
because Amazon reviews are

00:03:12.733 --> 00:03:14.599
generally much higher quality,

00:03:14.600 --> 00:03:16.100
especially the top ten.

00:03:16.100 --> 00:03:18.766
We should put more effort into

00:03:19.133 --> 00:03:20.299
creating high-quality content and

00:03:20.300 --> 00:03:22.533
avoid AliExpress reviews like "

00:03:22.533 --> 00:03:24.133
Great Good," as

00:03:24.366 --> 00:03:26.966
these are not very meaningful.

00:03:26.966 --> 00:03:29.466
There are also many review plugins available now that

00:03:29.466 --> 00:03:31.399
can import reviews from Amazon,

00:03:31.400 --> 00:03:33.266
or we can directly

00:03:33.266 --> 00:03:36.333
import reviews into our website using a spreadsheet. It

00:03:36.333 --> 00:03:37.666
might take a little time,

00:03:37.666 --> 00:03:39.799
but it's very worthwhile.

00:03:39.900 --> 00:03:42.100
We can see that this website's reviews are

00:03:42.266 --> 00:03:44.266
also imported from Amazon.

00:03:44.266 --> 00:03:45.466


00:03:45.466 --> 00:03:46.566
We can see that the

00:03:47.100 --> 00:03:50.800
Amazon name at the top hasn't been changed.

00:03:50.800 --> 00:03:51.866
We can also see

00:03:51.866 --> 00:03:53.333


00:03:53.333 --> 00:03:55.866
a verified badge under the reviewer's name,

00:03:56.200 --> 00:03:58.733
which can also be

00:03:58.900 --> 00:04:00.000
set using plugins.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:01.133
This website

00:04:01.133 --> 00:04:03.866
doesn't have many reviews,

00:04:03.866 --> 00:04:06.466
but each review usually

00:04:06.466 --> 00:04:07.999
includes several pictures,

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:10.500
which is quite convincing.

00:04:10.500 --> 00:04:14.666
Let's take a look at the price variations on the product details page

00:04:14.666 --> 00:04:15.666
and the shopping cart.

00:04:15.666 --> 00:04:16.899
These are all very basic,

00:04:16.900 --> 00:04:18.700
so there's not much to say. For the

00:04:18.700 --> 00:04:20.000
variations,

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:22.600
we should try to choose

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:24.533
templates that display thumbnails,

00:04:24.533 --> 00:04:27.133
as this makes it more intuitive.

00:04:27.200 --> 00:04:28.700
Of course,

00:04:28.900 --> 00:04:31.700
text display doesn't have as much impact. The

00:04:31.700 --> 00:04:34.000
fifth part is multi-item discounts.

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:37.500
Here, I usually

00:04:37.500 --> 00:04:39.200


00:04:39.400 --> 00:04:41.700
put multi-item discount information above or below the quantity,

00:04:41.733 --> 00:04:43.899
such as 5% off for buying two items,

00:04:43.900 --> 00:04:46.500
10% off for buying three items, and 15% off for buying five items.

00:04:46.766 --> 00:04:49.266
This is a great way to increase the average order value

00:04:49.533 --> 00:04:50.333
because we all know that

00:04:50.333 --> 00:04:51.966
traffic is hard-earned.

00:04:51.966 --> 00:04:54.099
If you can

00:04:54.100 --> 00:04:56.100
generate a higher average order value from the traffic you attract,

00:04:56.266 --> 00:04:58.966
it's a very important way to increase our sales.

00:04:59.100 --> 00:05:00.100


00:05:00.100 --> 00:05:02.000
This method

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:03.766
is very good for both us and the buyers

00:05:03.933 --> 00:05:05.899
because while we are giving discounts to buyers,

00:05:05.900 --> 00:05:08.933
we are also saving a lot of costs.

00:05:08.966 --> 00:05:11.066
From my historical data,

00:05:11.066 --> 00:05:11.966
about

00:05:11.966 --> 00:05:14.733
1-2 out of every 10 orders have

00:05:15.166 --> 00:05:16.733
multiple items. The

00:05:16.733 --> 00:05:18.733
sixth part is upselling, which is

00:05:18.766 --> 00:05:21.866
another way to increase the average order value. It involves

00:05:22.166 --> 00:05:24.466
recommending other related products in our store to buyers, offering

00:05:24.466 --> 00:05:25.933


00:05:25.933 --> 00:05:26.733


00:05:26.933 --> 00:05:30.266
more discounts when purchased together.

00:05:30.266 --> 00:05:31.266
This store

00:05:31.266 --> 00:05:33.299
also uses this method.

00:05:33.700 --> 00:05:36.133
It combines these three products, resulting in a

00:05:36.133 --> 00:05:38.799
lower total price. The

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:41.066
seventh part is the payment method,

00:05:41.200 --> 00:05:44.100
which is a common headache for many sellers.

00:05:44.133 --> 00:05:45.466
Domestic sellers often have limited

00:05:45.466 --> 00:05:48.599
payment options.

00:05:48.966 --> 00:05:50.699
Many independent sellers

00:05:50.700 --> 00:05:53.500
can only offer PayPal

00:05:53.766 --> 00:05:56.099
because it's relatively easy to apply for. However,

00:05:56.100 --> 00:05:56.966


00:05:56.966 --> 00:05:59.266
while PayPal is widely used,

00:05:59.700 --> 00:06:02.733
offering more payment methods is always better.

00:06:02.733 --> 00:06:03.999
For example, credit card payments

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:04.566
or

00:06:04.566 --> 00:06:07.566
BNPL (Bill of Materials), which is popular internationally, are

00:06:07.566 --> 00:06:08.566
also options.

00:06:08.566 --> 00:06:10.266
Offering these payment methods is

00:06:10.266 --> 00:06:13.099
a significant advantage. The

00:06:13.133 --> 00:06:15.299
eighth part covers our

00:06:15.400 --> 00:06:16.966
service guarantees,

00:06:17.333 --> 00:06:19.466
delivery time,

00:06:19.466 --> 00:06:21.899
product shelf life,

00:06:22.300 --> 00:06:23.766
and

00:06:23.766 --> 00:06:26.533
return/exchange policies.

00:06:26.533 --> 00:06:29.166
Buyers value

00:06:29.166 --> 00:06:30.999
these information, so it's

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:34.933
best to place them below the purchase button to

00:06:34.933 --> 00:06:38.299
increase website

00:06:38.300 --> 00:06:38.933
credibility. The

00:06:38.933 --> 00:06:41.866
ninth part, a

00:06:42.366 --> 00:06:44.466
crucial section of the product page, is the

00:06:44.566 --> 00:06:45.733
product description.

00:06:46.133 --> 00:06:48.166
This

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:51.166
description showcases the product's highlights to attract buyers and

00:06:51.200 --> 00:06:54.500
addresses potential

00:06:54.933 --> 00:06:57.066
issues they might encounter during the purchase process.

00:06:57.066 --> 00:06:59.666
We try to put eye-catching features and

00:06:59.666 --> 00:07:01.199
highlights at the beginning. As for

00:07:01.200 --> 00:07:02.566
detailed specifications,

00:07:02.566 --> 00:07:05.133
such as size,

00:07:05.566 --> 00:07:06.666
color,

00:07:06.733 --> 00:07:09.599
and packaging,

00:07:09.666 --> 00:07:11.766
we try to place them later on the website.

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:12.333
We know that

00:07:12.333 --> 00:07:14.399
buyers' attention spans are limited,

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:16.200
so we try not to put these

00:07:16.200 --> 00:07:18.966
relatively basic information first.

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:21.466
Because when they are truly interested in your product, they will

00:07:21.466 --> 00:07:24.499
definitely browse the entire page,

00:07:24.500 --> 00:07:26.766
including actively searching for

00:07:26.766 --> 00:07:28.599
information they want to know,

00:07:28.866 --> 00:07:30.933
such as usage instructions, the contents of the

00:07:30.933 --> 00:07:33.966
package, and

00:07:33.966 --> 00:07:34.799


00:07:34.800 --> 00:07:36.500
detailed specifications.

00:07:36.500 --> 00:07:38.400
We also try to use

00:07:38.400 --> 00:07:39.533
animated GIFs.

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:42.466
Shopify has always supported animated GIFs, which makes the

00:07:42.733 --> 00:07:44.533
content

00:07:44.700 --> 00:07:46.266
more attractive and effectively

00:07:46.300 --> 00:07:46.933


00:07:46.933 --> 00:07:50.066
conveys the product's usage and features. For

00:07:50.066 --> 00:07:50.999
these animated GIFs,

00:07:51.000 --> 00:07:52.766
we can find product videos

00:07:52.766 --> 00:07:54.966
or buy samples and

00:07:54.966 --> 00:07:56.466
shoot our own videos, then use

00:07:56.466 --> 00:07:57.599


00:07:57.933 --> 00:07:58.899
GIF tools to

00:07:58.900 --> 00:08:01.700
extract the GIFs.

00:08:01.766 --> 00:08:03.699
If you have product videos,

00:08:03.700 --> 00:08:06.100
you can also put them on the description page,

00:08:06.166 --> 00:08:08.866
but remember not to make them too long, preferably

00:08:08.866 --> 00:08:10.366
no more than one minute.

00:08:10.466 --> 00:08:12.099
We can see that this

00:08:12.100 --> 00:08:14.600
description is relatively high-end,

00:08:15.566 --> 00:08:18.099
like this detail page layout.  It

00:08:18.100 --> 00:08:20.266
's related to its template,

00:08:20.333 --> 00:08:22.999
but its content is indeed very professional

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:24.666
and technologically advanced,

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:27.800
including its details. The

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:30.333
product descriptions also utilize rendering techniques,

00:08:30.933 --> 00:08:33.599
and the detailed information is very well done, with

00:08:33.600 --> 00:08:36.100
more detailed information

00:08:36.100 --> 00:08:37.200
placed at the end.

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:39.200
Let's look at another website; its

00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:40.200


00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:43.333
description is relatively simpler

00:08:43.966 --> 00:08:44.966
because its product description is also relatively

00:08:44.966 --> 00:08:46.533
simple.

00:08:46.566 --> 00:08:48.333
However, it still covers the important points,

00:08:48.333 --> 00:08:50.933
including how to use the product and its

00:08:51.366 --> 00:08:53.266
detailed information.

00:08:53.266 --> 00:08:54.666
If your current conditions

00:08:54.666 --> 00:08:56.799
don't allow for a product

00:08:56.800 --> 00:08:57.600
detail page like the one above,

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:59.766
I think creating something like the one below is

00:08:59.933 --> 00:09:01.199
also acceptable.

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:03.166
Part 10 is the FAQ, which contains

00:09:03.166 --> 00:09:06.199
frequently asked questions and answers.

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:09.000
This part is easily overlooked,

00:09:09.366 --> 00:09:11.799
but its advantage is that

00:09:11.800 --> 00:09:13.400


00:09:13.400 --> 00:09:15.766
buyers can find answers to common questions directly here

00:09:15.900 --> 00:09:17.466
without having to contact us,

00:09:17.466 --> 00:09:19.733
thus increasing response speed.

00:09:19.933 --> 00:09:21.199
Since our

00:09:21.266 --> 00:09:23.299
main consumer market is overseas, there's

00:09:23.300 --> 00:09:25.900
definitely a time difference.

00:09:25.900 --> 00:09:28.466
We can't be online 24/7. By the

00:09:28.466 --> 00:09:29.899
time we realize a buyer has a question, we

00:09:29.900 --> 00:09:30.900


00:09:30.900 --> 00:09:33.000
may have already missed the best sales opportunity.

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:33.666
Therefore, it's

00:09:33.666 --> 00:09:35.733
best to summarize and compile some common questions.

00:09:35.733 --> 00:09:36.933


00:09:36.933 --> 00:09:39.966
Place it below our product description.

00:09:39.966 --> 00:09:41.866
When users browsing our website

00:09:41.866 --> 00:09:43.499
are interested in our products

00:09:43.500 --> 00:09:44.966
and encounter problems,

00:09:45.166 --> 00:09:48.399
if they can find answers below,

00:09:48.566 --> 00:09:52.466
they are more likely to place an order.

00:09:52.500 --> 00:09:53.966
We can see that this website

00:09:53.966 --> 00:09:56.366
not only includes frequently asked questions, but

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:58.666
also shipping policies,

00:09:58.666 --> 00:10:00.666
guarantees, and other

00:10:00.900 --> 00:10:04.266
information.

00:10:04.600 --> 00:10:05.900
It also

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:08.733
includes a download button for the instruction manual,

00:10:08.733 --> 00:10:10.299
which is very thoughtful.

00:10:10.300 --> 00:10:11.600
Firstly,

00:10:11.766 --> 00:10:13.799
some people may not have bought your product yet,

00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:16.066
but they can look at the manual first and

00:10:16.066 --> 00:10:17.699


00:10:17.700 --> 00:10:19.800
discover some advantages of the product, leading to a

00:10:19.800 --> 00:10:21.200
purchase.

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:22.533
Secondly, and quite strangely,

00:10:22.533 --> 00:10:24.166
many overseas buyers

00:10:24.600 --> 00:10:26.733
always ask for the instruction manual after receiving the product,

00:10:26.866 --> 00:10:28.399


00:10:28.766 --> 00:10:30.799


00:10:30.900 --> 00:10:32.666


00:10:32.666 --> 00:10:34.499
even if you've included it in the product description.

00:10:34.500 --> 00:10:36.066
Therefore,

00:10:36.066 --> 00:10:38.799
including a download link for the instruction manual on the website

00:10:38.800 --> 00:10:41.400
saves us a lot of after-sales time

00:10:41.400 --> 00:10:42.900
and

00:10:43.366 --> 00:10:45.466
increases customer satisfaction.

00:10:45.466 --> 00:10:47.399
So, the FAQ section is

00:10:47.400 --> 00:10:49.766
relatively important. Regarding

00:10:49.766 --> 00:10:51.899
section 11, online chat,

00:10:52.466 --> 00:10:53.333


00:10:53.333 --> 00:10:55.366
I don't recommend including

00:10:55.366 --> 00:10:56.733
real-time chat tools. This is due to the

00:10:57.066 --> 00:10:59.133
issue mentioned above;

00:10:59.133 --> 00:11:02.066
if you can't handle time zone differences...

00:11:02.400 --> 00:11:04.966
In other words, if you can't respond to buyer questions in real time,

00:11:05.266 --> 00:11:06.799


00:11:06.966 --> 00:11:09.533
you don't need to add such a tool.

00:11:09.533 --> 00:11:11.499
You can simply use a

00:11:11.966 --> 00:11:13.766
self-service solution

00:11:13.766 --> 00:11:15.999
and put it in our FAQ. The

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:18.766
twelfth part is recommended products.

00:11:18.766 --> 00:11:20.999
I usually put this part

00:11:21.100 --> 00:11:22.500
above the comments section. Here, it's

00:11:22.500 --> 00:11:24.366
placed below. The

00:11:24.366 --> 00:11:25.866
main purpose is to increase the

00:11:25.866 --> 00:11:27.699
exposure of other products in the store and

00:11:27.733 --> 00:11:30.066
potentially

00:11:30.333 --> 00:11:31.333
increase our sales.

00:11:31.333 --> 00:11:32.333
This website also has a

00:11:32.333 --> 00:11:34.133
good feature:

00:11:34.133 --> 00:11:35.933


00:11:35.933 --> 00:11:37.666
a comparison of different models of similar products.

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:39.933
This is a pretty good function.

00:11:39.966 --> 00:11:41.133
However, if you want to

00:11:41.133 --> 00:11:43.199
add such a function to the website, it

00:11:43.200 --> 00:11:45.866
may involve some code modifications.

00:11:45.866 --> 00:11:46.199
So, if

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:48.200
you want to add such a comparison module,

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:50.666
you need to consider whether you can create it yourself. The

00:11:50.666 --> 00:11:53.733
above are basically the elements that a qualified product details page should

00:11:53.733 --> 00:11:55.333
have.

00:11:55.500 --> 00:11:57.066
As for other functions,

00:11:57.066 --> 00:11:58.299
for example, many people

00:11:58.300 --> 00:12:00.100
sometimes

00:12:00.100 --> 00:12:01.466


00:12:01.466 --> 00:12:02.666
add

00:12:02.866 --> 00:12:04.733
countdown discounts or similar functions below the product price.

00:12:05.133 --> 00:12:07.299
You can decide whether to include this or not based on your needs, or whether

00:12:07.300 --> 00:12:08.200


00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:10.866
you can find some plugins

00:12:10.866 --> 00:12:12.166
to implement such functions.

00:12:12.166 --> 00:12:14.899
Also, our details page should not be

00:12:14.933 --> 00:12:16.966
piled with various marketing tools. You ca

00:12:17.200 --> 00:12:19.166
n't just put up whatever tool

00:12:19.166 --> 00:12:20.166


00:12:20.166 --> 00:12:21.566
you think is good.

00:12:21.566 --> 00:12:22.599
Actually, it's unnecessary

00:12:22.700 --> 00:12:23.566
because doing so

00:12:23.566 --> 00:12:26.099
will affect the loading speed and aesthetics of our webpage, potentially having the opposite

00:12:26.100 --> 00:12:27.666
effect.

00:12:27.666 --> 00:12:28.899


00:12:28.900 --> 00:12:30.166
Finally, another very important point

00:12:30.166 --> 00:12:31.699
is mobile compatibility.

00:12:31.866 --> 00:12:33.599
Historical data shows that

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:35.600
about 80% of users

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:37.866
shop online using mobile devices.

00:12:37.866 --> 00:12:40.799
Therefore, regardless of whether it's a computer or mobile device,

00:12:40.800 --> 00:12:43.666
we need to ensure the page layout is effective.

00:12:43.700 --> 00:12:45.133
Most templates now

00:12:45.133 --> 00:12:46.766
support mobile devices and

00:12:46.766 --> 00:12:48.999
will automatically adapt to your products.

00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:50.466
However, to see the actual effect,

00:12:50.466 --> 00:12:52.299
we still need to check it ourselves.

00:12:52.300 --> 00:12:53.300
A simple method is to

00:12:53.300 --> 00:12:55.500


00:12:55.500 --> 00:12:57.800
open the store's URL on your mobile phone to see the effect. Alternatively,

00:12:57.800 --> 00:13:00.600
we can use Google Chrome to

00:13:00.666 --> 00:13:02.766
simulate a mobile effect.

00:13:02.800 --> 00:13:04.900
Right-click on the current webpage

00:13:04.900 --> 00:13:06.200
and select "Inspect."

00:13:06.200 --> 00:13:08.733
Some code will appear on the right, with

00:13:08.733 --> 00:13:09.399


00:13:09.400 --> 00:13:12.000
a phone and tablet icon above it.

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.800
Clicking this will

00:13:13.800 --> 00:13:15.400
simulate a mobile device.

00:13:15.400 --> 00:13:16.166
Above this icon,

00:13:16.166 --> 00:13:18.899
we can select phone models,

00:13:18.900 --> 00:13:20.933
sizes,

00:13:20.933 --> 00:13:22.733
and adjust the aspect ratio

00:13:22.733 --> 00:13:24.166
and rotation. We

00:13:24.166 --> 00:13:25.933


00:13:25.933 --> 00:13:27.733


00:13:27.733 --> 00:13:28.666


00:13:28.700 --> 00:13:30.500
can then preview the overall display on a mobile device to ensure our webpage

00:13:30.500 --> 00:13:32.333
displays correctly. Overall, there are

00:13:32.333 --> 00:13:33.166


00:13:33.166 --> 00:13:34.766
n't many problems, and the

00:13:34.766 --> 00:13:37.533
mobile display is quite nice.

00:13:37.533 --> 00:13:39.299
That concludes this episode.

00:13:39.300 --> 00:13:42.466
